node.detail_zh: 患者任職海員，過往健康良好，1 月至 7 月 10 日在菲律賓，搭乘國泰航空 CX906 抵港。7 月 3 日開始發燒及咳嗽，由港口衞生料轉介送院。
node.detail_en: The patient is a sailor with good past health and was in the Philippines between January and July 10. He arrived in Hong Kong via Cathay Pacific flight CX906. On July 3, he started having fever and cough. He was transferred to hospital from the Port Health Division.
